              "reading_order": 7,
              "subsections": []
            },
            {
              "title": "G. MATCHING, LEVEL OF EFFORT, EARMARKING",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "list",
                  "list_type": "ordered",
                  "items": [
                    {
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "text": "Matching: The Federal government will pay 80% of the total amount of funds expended by DSS up to \\the amount Chafee ETV funds allocated to NC. DSS must provide matching contributions to cover the additional 20% of the costs. This is a mandatory grant requirement. DSS is responsible for certifying the 20% match by documenting the required amount spent on the eligible foster care population.",
                          "bold": false,
