                    {
                      "text": "Subrecipients are monitored by the NC State LINKS Program in accordance to the NC Department of Health and Human Services, Division of Social Services Subrecipient Monitoring Plan – Contracts, found at: NC Sub-Recipient Monitoring Plan.",
